          "settings": {
            "title": "CELEBRATING 25 YEARS WITH YOU"
          }
        },
        "text_hxzxUg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "enlarge_text": true,
            "text": "<p>Twenty-five years ago, Charlotte & Grace Boutique began as a small dream shared between a mother and daughter. What started as a passion for timeless fashion slowly grew into a boutique filled with wonderful women, beautiful memories, and styles we truly love.</p><p>This anniversary sale is our way of saying thank you for being part of our journey over the past 25 years.</p><p>To celebrate this special milestone, enjoy up to <strong>70% OFF</strong> our most loved collections for a limited time.</p><p>Every piece is chosen with the same care and passion we started with all those years ago — to help women feel confident, elegant, and comfortable every day.</p><p>With love ♥<br/><br/>— Charlotte & Grace Boutique</p>"
          }
        }
      },
