        "subtitle": "",
        "title": "Our Story — Charlotte & Grace Boutique",
        "text": "<p>25 years ago, Charlotte opened a small boutique in New York with one simple dream: helping women feel beautiful and confident. ✨</p><p>When her daughter Grace turned 16, she began helping in the store after school, and together they turned their shared passion for fashion into something truly special.</p><p>Today, Charlotte & Grace Boutique has grown into a beloved online boutique, but our mission remains the same:<br/><br/>creating elegant, timeless fashion that makes women feel confident every day. 🤍</p><p>Thank you for being part of our journey.</p><p>With love,<br/><br/>Charlotte & Grace ✨</p>",
        "button_label": "",
